{
  "stem": "16214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was quite starved at the time, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she didn't want to stay at the station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she walked out, evidently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so a little shop very close by-- and she walked in there and she said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Christ be with you-- which, you know, normal sort of saying, God be with you-- a little Roman Catholic saying, something.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, I am with my daughter going to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Goleniow. ?] And the train just left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And could I possibly stay with her here, because she's a little sick?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- you know, I can't stay at the station with her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the lady was very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, absolutely, but not here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can stay in our room, which is in the back of the store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was very helpful to my mother-- gave her food, gave me food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, at night, she sent her husband with my mother to the train station so she doesn't, you know, look suspicious that she's just going by herself-- not knowing, of course, that she's Jewish, but just not to be by herself, a woman alone with a child.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the gentleman escorted her to the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my mother-- luckily, without any documents-- was not stopped, and was able to arrive to the village or small town of [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Goleniow, ?] where my father's brother was living and where my mother expected that my father would be there by that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when she arrived, my father-- she found out that my father already left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was not there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the first thing-- they were so terrified, everybody, when they saw my mother and me.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
